        "management": "NSAIDs + non-opioid analgesics (WHO Step 1). Weak opioids (codeine, tramadol) (Step 2). Strong opioids (morphine, oxycodone) (Step 3). Adjuvant therapies (bisphosphonates for bone pain, RT)."
