        "management": "Adjuvant analgesics: gabapentinoids (gabapentin, pregabalin), tricyclic antidepressants (amitriptyline), SNRIs (duloxetine). Opioids often needed. Nerve blocks. Palliative RT. Ketamine infusion for refractory cases."
